OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772741480
OL,3,CMan jailed for calling 999 then
OL,4,Cthreatening paramedic with imitation
OL,5,Cfirearm
OL,7,FA man has been jailed after he pointed
OL,8,Fan imitation firearm at a paramedic's
OL,9,Fface who was trying to help him.
OL,11,FClive Monamy dialled 999 on the
OL,12,Fevening of 5 May, 2024, and requested
OL,13,Fan ambulance due to his mental health.
OL,15,FA South East Coast Ambulance employee
OL,16,Fresponded to the address in Hide
OL,17,FGardens, Rustington, and was met with
OL,18,Fa barrage of abuse from Monamy.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
