OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772741480
OL,3,CMan jailed for calling 999 then
OL,4,Cthreatening paramedic with imitation
OL,5,Cfirearm
OL,7,FHe refused any treatment, despite
OL,8,Frequesting it by telephone and so the
OL,9,Fparamedic decided to leave the address.
OL,11,FAs he did so, the defendant said: "I
OL,12,Fhave something for you," and produced
OL,13,Fa black handgun from beneath a pillow
OL,14,Fand pointed it directly in the
OL,15,Fvictim's face.
OL,17,FActing on instinct, the paramedic
OL,18,Flunged at Monamy and disarmed him,
OL,19,Fbefore fleeing the address and calling
OL,20,Fpolice.
OL,26,@sD@cOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772741480
OL,3,CMan jailed for calling 999 then
OL,4,Cthreatening paramedic with imitation
OL,5,Cfirearm
OL,7,FOfficers attended and located the
OL,8,Fweapon, which was confirmed to be a BB
OL,9,Fgun.
OL,11,FThey arrested the 65-year-old, who was
OL,12,Fsubsequently charged with possession
OL,13,Fof an imitation firearm with intent to
OL,14,Fcause fear of violence.
OL,16,FMonamy, who is retired, pleaded guilty
OL,17,Fand was sentenced to 20 months'
OL,18,Fimprisonment at Lewes Crown Court on
OL,19,F27 February.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
