OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772741480
OL,3,CMan jailed for calling 999 then
OL,4,Cthreatening paramedic with imitation
OL,5,Cfirearm
OL,7,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,8,FConstable Neil Winter, said: "This
OL,9,Fincident caused the paramedic to
OL,10,Fexperience extreme distress, at a time
OL,11,Fwhen he was responding to the
OL,12,Fdefendant's call for assistance.
OL,14,F"Irrespective of his circumstances,
OL,15,Fthis was a serious offence which
OL,16,Fgenuinely caused the victim to fear
OL,17,Ffor his life.
OL,26,@pD@^OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
