OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772741480
OL,3,CMan jailed for calling 999 then
OL,4,Cthreatening paramedic with imitation
OL,5,Cfirearm
OL,7,F"This sort of behaviour towards
OL,8,Femergency workers ` or any member of
OL,9,Fthe public for that matter ` is
OL,10,Ftotally unacceptable and any offenders
OL,11,Fcan expect to be dealt with robustly
OL,12,Fby the courts."
OL,14,FSouth East Coast Ambulance Service
OL,15,FSecurity Manager, David Monk, said:
OL,16,F"Our frontline colleagues attend
OL,17,Fincidents to provide care and
OL,18,Fcompassion to those in need, and they
OL,19,Fshould never have to face threats or
OL,20,Fviolence while doing their job.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@OO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
