OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1772741480
OL,3,CMan jailed for calling 999 then
OL,4,Cthreatening paramedic with imitation
OL,5,Cfirearm
OL,7,F"This was an extremely frightening
OL,8,Fordeal for our colleague, who was
OL,9,Fsimply responding to a call for help.
OL,10,FWe will always work closely with the
OL,11,Fpolice to ensure that anyone who puts
OL,12,Four staff at risk is held fully
OL,13,Faccountable for their actions."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@_O]
